LINK_SEARCH_SETTINGS.linkSummaryInput: <title-text>OIC Service Instances</title-text> <title-text>Projects</title-text> <title-text>Total Integrations</title-text> <title-text>Transactions</title-text> <title-text>Integration Instances</title-text>

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and 'Transaction ID' != null | link Entity | addfields [ 'Project ID' = null and Identifier != null | stats distinctcount(Identifier) as 'standalone-integs' ] | eventstats distinctcount(Entity) as 'OIC Service Instances', distinctcount('Project ID') as 'Unique Projects', distinctcount('OPC Request ID') as 'Unique Transactions', distinctcount(Identifier) as 'Unique Integrations', distinctcount(Instance) as 'Instance Execs', sum('standalone-integs') as 'Standalone Integrations' | fields -Count, -'standalone-integs', -'Start Time', -'End Time'

'Action Type' in (Invoke, Log, Notification, Raise_error, Submitnow, Stop, Switch, Raise_new_error, Receive) and 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and Identifier != null and 'OPC Request ID' != null | stats count(Action) as Milestones by Action

'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and 'Action Type' in (Invoke, Log, Notification, Raise_error, Submitnow, Stop, Switch, Raise_new_error, Receive) and Identifier != null | link 'OPC Request ID', 'Transaction ID' | rename 'Group Duration' as 'Transaction Time' | sequence name = Milestones [ Action != null and 'Action Type' != null and 'Event ID' != null ]{1,} select Action, 'Action Type', 'Event ID', Integration | stats latest(Integration) as Integration, latest(Action) as 'Latest Action', unique('OIC Project') as 'Project Name', distinctcount(Identifier) as Integrations, unique(Entity) as Entity, unique(Instance) as Instance | classify correlate = -*, Integration, 'Project Name', 'Transaction ID' 'Start Time', 'Latest Action', 'Transaction Time' as 'Transaction Execution Time' | fields target = ui -'OPC Request ID', -Entity, -Instance

'Action Type' in (Invoke, Log, Notification, Raise_error, Submitnow, Stop, Switch, Raise_new_error, Receive) and 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' | timestats count(Action) as Milestones by Action
'Log Source' = 'Fusion Apps: Sign-in Sign-Out Activity' | stats count as 'Login Events ' by Status | sort -Status

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'Oracle Fusion Apps: Enterprise Scheduler Service (ESS)' | link 'Request ID' | stats unique(Application) as Application, avg(ElapsedTime) as E, unique('Instance Parent Id') as 'Parent ID', unique('Job Display Name') as Job, unique('Parent Request ID') as 'Parent Req ID', unique(Product) as Product, latest('State Description') as Status, unique(Submitter) as Submitter | eval 'Time Taken' = unit(E, ms) | eval U = url('https://oracle.com', View) | eventstats distinctcount('Request ID') as Requests, avg(E) as AE, latest(U) as Details by Product, Job, Status | eval 'Average Time Taken' = unit(AE, ms) | createtable name = 'Job Summary' select Product, Job, Status, Requests, 'Average Time Taken', Details | classify 'Start Time', Job, 'Time Taken', Product, Status as 'ESS Jobs Analysis' | fields -E, -AE
